---
import '../styles/global.css';
// Import favicon assets
import favicon from '../assets/favicon.svg';
import favicon96 from '../assets/favicon-96x96.png';
import faviconIco from '../assets/favicon.ico';
import appleIcon from '../assets/apple-touch-icon.png';
// Import site manifest
import siteManifest from '../assets/site.webmanifest';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Now - William L. Anderson</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={favicon96.src} sizes="96x96" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href={favicon.src} />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href={faviconIco.src} />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href={appleIcon.src} />
    <link rel="manifest" href={siteManifest.src} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <style>
      #now {
        padding: 0;
      }
      .now-intro {
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .now-intro h1 {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }
      .now-intro p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .now-section {
        margin: 1rem 0;
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .now-section h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        padding-bottom: 0;
        padding-top: 0;
        border-top: none;
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      #now p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .now-section ul {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
      }
      .now-section ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      #now .site-footer {
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
      }
    </style>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
            <span class="brand-full">William L. Anderson</span>
            <span class="brand-short">Will Anderson</span>
        </a>
        <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" id="mobileMenuToggle">☰</button>
        <ul class="navbar-links" id="navbarLinks">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/now">Now</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/william-l-anderson-a853b92aa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/wlanderson0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://wlandersons.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Substack</a></li>
            <li><a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resume</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <main class="container">
      <section id="now">
        <div class="now-intro">
          <h1>What am I up to now?</h1>
          <p>This is a "<a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">now page</a>." You should make one too!</p>
          <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666;">Last updated 12/16/25, from my childhood home in Minnesota.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="now-section">
          <h2>Work and Such</h2>
          <p>Most of my time right now is focused on preparing for MATS, which means:</p>
          <ul class="simple-list">
            <li>Frantically finishing as many projects as possible before I start more.</li>
            <li>Grappling with the fact that I'm done with school, the institution which has set the rhythm of my entire remembered life.</li>
            <li>Thinking a lot about the importance-to-volume-ratio of my possessions in preparation for living out of suitcase.</li>
            <li>Trying to create a smooth transition for WAISI leadership. The churn of student groups is insane, but I really believe in the team.</li>
            <li>Saying goodbye to many of my dearest friends, while scheming ways to keep in touch.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      
        <div class="now-section">
          <h2>That other part of life that I forget about</h2>
          <p>My aunt got me a tea advent calendar, so I've gotten to try many new teas. Big fan of piccadilly, vanilla chai, and masala chai. I've been watching (and plan to start reading/playing) The Witcher. I've also been reflecting on a year of incredible personal and professional change. The shape of my life is not even remotely what it was a year ago. I'm excited to see where 2026 takes me!</p>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 2rem;"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
      </section>

      <footer class="site-footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 William L. Anderson. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>

    <script>
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
          // Mobile menu functionality
          const mobileToggle = document.getElementById('mobileMenuToggle');
          const navbarLinks = document.getElementById('navbarLinks');

          if (mobileToggle && navbarLinks) {
            mobileToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
              navbarLinks.classList.toggle('active');
            });
          }

          // Close mobile menu when clicking outside
          document.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
            if (
              navbarLinks &&
              mobileToggle &&
              !navbarLinks.contains(event.target as Node) &&
              !mobileToggle.contains(event.target as Node)
            ) {
              navbarLinks.classList.remove('active');
            }
          });
        });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
